
# 🔹 5. Structured Output (JSON)

## 📖 Concept

Used for **machine-readable responses** (APIs, automation).

---

## 🧾 Prompt

```
Extract name and age in JSON:

"Ravi is 28 years old"
```

---

## 💻 LLM Code

```python
response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="gpt-5.3",
    messages=[
        {"role": "user", "content": "Extract name and age from: Ravi is 28 years old"}
    ],
    response_format={"type": "json_object"}
)

print(response.choices[0].message.content)
```

---

## ✅ Output

```json
{
  "name": "Ravi",
  "age": 28
}
```

